Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Swordsage level 1st.
Specifics: Increase the number of maneuvers you can ready for your swordsage levels by one. For example, a 5th-level swordsage can normally ready six maneuvers. With this feat, she can ready seven.

Use: Automatic.

Special: This feat applies only to maneuvers readied by Swordsages.